nese/files/2019/03/7-12-300x184.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/7-12-768x471.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/7-12-1024x628.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/7-12-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>补充两个信中删减了的例子，一同体会一波：</p>\n<blockquote><p>农奴问喇嘛，为什么我像畜生一样活着，眼睛被你们挖去祭菩萨，老爷却穿金戴银住碉堡？</p>\n<p>喇嘛说，因为你前世造了孽，你要忍耐这一切，才能赎罪。要是赎罪了，下辈子就好了！</p>\n<p>工人问神父，为什么我工资月月光，天天加班到半夜，没有休息日，没有五险一金，而资本家住着别墅搂着小老婆开着法拉利度假？</p>\n<p>神父说，我父的子民都是平等的，那些物质的快乐都是虚妄，内心的愉悦才是真实。忘掉那些东西，感受我父赐予你内心的平静与喜悦吧！</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-608071\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8-11.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8-11-300x254.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8-11-768x651.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8-11-1024x868.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p></blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-608072\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-8.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-8-300x113.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-8-768x289.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-8-1024x385.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-608073\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/10-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"588\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/10-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/10-4-255x300.jpg 255w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/10-4-768x9